               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾāmra ʾIyasus “Miracles of Jesus” (fols. 1ra-98rb)&#xD; I-1)
                     ʾƎsaggǝd la-malakotǝka… “I worship Thy Godhead…” (fols. 1ra-2rb)&#xD; I-2)
                     Introduction (fols. 3ra-7vb)&#xD; - On John the Evangelist as the author of the
                     book; on the creation and the fall of the angels (fols. 3ra-5ra)&#xD; - Story
                     of the family of Adam (fols. 5ra-7vb)&#xD; I-3) Taʾāmra ʾIyasus “Miracles of
                     Jesus”: 75 miracles (fols. 7vb-98rb) &#xD; &#xD; Additiones 1-3.</summary>
